###############################################################################
# 📚 FASE 6 - EMPRÉSTIMOS (LOANS)
###############################################################################

### 30. Criar empréstimo (emprestar livro)
# Emprestar "Clean Code" para João Silva (usuário ID 1)
# Requer: JWT de ADMIN ou LIBRARIAN
POST {{baseUrl}}/loans
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "bookId": 1,
  "dueDate": "2026-03-15"
}

### 31. Criar empréstimo sem dueDate (usa padrão: +14 dias)
POST {{baseUrl}}/loans
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "bookId": 2
}

### 32. Listar todos os empréstimos
GET {{baseUrl}}/loans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 33. Listar empréstimos de um usuário específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/loans?userId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 34. Listar empréstimos ativos
GET {{baseUrl}}/loans?status=ACTIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 35. Listar empréstimos com paginação
GET {{baseUrl}}/loans?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 36. Listar empréstimos de um livro (histórico)
GET {{baseUrl}}/loans?bookId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 37. Listar empréstimos por período
GET {{baseUrl}}/loans?loanDateFrom=2026-02-01&loanDateTo=2026-02-28
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 38. Buscar empréstimo por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/loans/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

