GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations?status=PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 49. Listar reservas de um livro (fila de espera)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations?bookId=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 50. Buscar reserva por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 51. Obter fila de espera de um livro
